response.overview: On July 29th GCW presents The People vs GCW live on FITE straight from Nashville Fairgrounds. The event features GCW World Title match where Jon Moxley will defend his title agains Blake Christian.  Also in the lineup:  Psycho Clown vs Joey Janela  Kevin Blackwood vs Masha Slamovich  Six Man Tag Team Match  Black Taurus, Gringo Loco & Jack Cartwheel vs ASF, Komander & Laredo Kid  Alex Zayne vs Nick Wayne  GCW Tag Team Title Three Way Match  BUSSY (Allie Katch & Effy) (c) vs Los Mazisos (Ciclope & Miedo Extremo) vs The Second Gear Crew (Mance Warner & Matthew Justice)  Bandido vs Jordan Oliver  Mike Bailey vs Tony Deppen
response.title: GCW The People vs GCW
